    "description": "<i>来感受班班的幼儿园的恐怖吧！深入探索这个空荡荡的可疑之地。试着从那些意想不到的居民中生存下来，并寻找你的孩子......</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311190/extras/4214e84d2b143ff2a328cd89260c0f4e.poster.avif?t=1756371468\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311190/extras/4214e84d2b143ff2a328cd89260c0f4e.webm?t=1756371468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311190/extras/4214e84d2b143ff2a328cd89260c0f4e.mp4?t=1756371468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深入探索班班幼儿园的深处：</h2></strong>班班的幼儿园这个神秘场所的深处比任何人想象的都要大，就像第一个游戏中看似无辜的幼儿园下面已经建了很多层。随着朋友的出现，你别无选择，只能继续深入这个地方，希望能找到你的孩子。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311190/extras/707b22f63fb00df99f9efd096d87d4c3.poster.avif?t=1756371468\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311190/extras/707b22f63fb00df99f9efd096d87d4c3.webm?t=1756371468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311190/extras/707b22f63fb00df99f9efd096d87d4c3.mp4?t=1756371468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311190/extras/83c16e58507bd06821d8a0f844efefa3.poster.avif?t=1756371468\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311190/extras/83c16e58507bd06821d8a0f844efefa3.webm?t=1756371468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311190/extras/83c16e58507bd06821d8a0f844efefa3.mp4?t=1756371468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >事实证明，交朋友并不是那么容易!</h2></strong>尽管你有很多机会交朋友，但你还是每次都失败。但随着你对这个场所的深入探索，也许你会在更底层获得成功。在班班的幼儿园里，你在每个角落都可以交到朋友!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311190/extras/ecb63af8fc1f2ad6e0b2509634a14660.poster.avif?t=1756371468\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311190/extras/ecb63af8fc1f2ad6e0b2509634a14660.webm?t=1756371468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311190/extras/ecb63af8fc1f2ad6e0b2509634a14660.mp4?t=1756371468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311190/extras/8fcca60de2f30be648e195687d8e5dba.poster.avif?t=1756371468\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311190/extras/8fcca60de2f30be648e195687d8e5dba.webm?t=1756371468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2311190/extras/8fcca60de2f30be648e195687d8e5dba.mp4?t=1756371468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>",
